ief Group|        Tampa|          Acupuncture|  1.0|              4.47|              -3.47|\n|                        BeStrong Fitness|         Reno|Fitness & Instruction|  1.0|              4.39|              -3.39|\n|Idaho Athletic Club Corporate & Membe...|        Eagle|          Active Life|  1.0|              4.39|              -3.39|\n|                               i9 Sports|    Tampa Bay|          Active Life|  1.0|              4.39|              -3.39|\n|      St. Louis Natural Treatment Center|  Saint Louis|        Chiropractors|  1.0|              4.36|              -3.36|\n|                   JG Estates Collection|    Montecito|        Home Services|  1.0|              4.36|              -3.36|\n|                     Liberty Pet Sitting| Philadelphia|          Pet Sitting|  1.0|              4.36|              -3.36|\n|                            The Dog Zone| Philadelphia|          Pet Sitting|  1.0|              4.36|              -3.36|\n|         Ed & Son's Painting and repairs| Philadelphia|     Pressure Washers|  1.0|              4.36|              -3.36|\n|                       Furniture By Brad|    Nashville|           Carpenters|  1.0|              4.33|              -3.33|\n|          Sunshine Carpet & Rug Cleaning|       Tucson|      Carpet Cleaning|  1.0|              4.33|              -3.33|\n|           Crescent City Auction Gallery|  New Orleans|        Art Galleries|  1.0|              4.32|              -3.32|\n|                            Tour America|   Clearwater|                Tours|  1.0|              4.32|              -3.32|\n+----------------------------------------+-------------+---------------------+-----+------------------+-------------------+\n\n"},{"type":"TABLE","data":"name\tcity\tcategory\tstars\tcategory_avg_stars\trating_differential\nTrunorth Photography\tBoise\tPhotographers\t1.0\t4.66\t-3.66\nTrunorth Photography\tBoise\tEvent Photography\t1.0\t4.6\t-3.6\nTrunorth Photography\tBoise\tSession Photography\t1.0\t4.